title: Assertion failed: !poly_trait_ref.needs_infer()

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

body:
rustc 1.15.0-nightly (1c448574b 2016-11-28)

```rust
#![feature(specialization)]

trait Iterate<'a> {
    type Ty: Valid;
    fn iterate(self);
}
impl<'a, T> Iterate<'a> for T where T: Check {
    default type Ty = ();
    default fn iterate(self) {}
}

trait Check {}
impl<'a, T> Check for T where <T as Iterate<'a>>::Ty: Valid {}

trait Valid {}

fn main() {
    Iterate::iterate(0);
}
```
